    public class SpringMyBatisCacheStore
extends AbstractSpringTransactionalCacheStore
    CacheStore implementation class integrated with Spring and MyBatis framework.
    This CacheStore is able to insert, update, delete, load to/from database through Coherence cache.
    Author:
    Shota Yamazaki
